    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "t = np.arange(0,10,0.05)\n",
        "y = np.exp(-0.5*t) * np.cos(2*np.pi*0.8*t)\n",
        "plt.figure()\n",
        "plt.plot(t, y, color= 'purple', linestyle= 'dashed')\n",
        "plt.grid()\n",
        "plt.title('gráfico da tensão em função do tempo')\n",
        "plt.xlabel('tempo em segundos')\n",
        "plt.ylabel('tensão elétrica')\n",
        "plt.show()"
      ],

        "import numpy as np\n",
        "import matplotlib.pyplot as plt\n",
        "a = np.arange(1994,2022,1)\n",
        "p = 800000*np.exp((a-1994) / 40)\n",
        "plt.figure()\n",
        "plt.plot(a, p, color= 'crimson', linestyle= 'dashdot')\n",
        "plt.grid()\n",
        "plt.title('gráfico do número de habitantes entre 1994 e 2022')\n",
        "plt.xlabel('ano')\n",
        "plt.ylabel('número de habitantes')\n",
        "plt.show()"
